istic Missile Defence Programme.''' 2000&nbsp;km range and flight ceiling of 50 to 80&nbsp;km.\n|-\n|[[Indian Ballistic Missile Defence Programme|Advance Air Defence]]\n|[[File:AAD Launch Crop.jpg|221x221px]]\n|[[Surface-to-air missile]]\n[[Anti-ballistic missile|Ballistic missile defence system]]\n|0\n|{{Flagu|India}}\n|'''Status: Testing/Induction Phase(Completed By 2016). '''It can be also used as Anti-aircraft missile.Last/final test to be held on May/June 2016. It has 150&nbsp;km range and flight ceiling of 30&nbsp;km.\n|-\n|[[S-400 (missile)|S-400 Triumf]]\n|[[File:S-400 Triumf launch vehicle.JPG|S-400|center|frameless]]\n|Mobile [[surface-to-air missile]] system\n|0\n|{{Flagu|Russia}}\n|'''Status:''' '''Ordered.'''  India's Cabinet Committee on Security(CCS) approved the deal, IGA formally signed. Order includes 5 battalions, consisting of Transporter Erector Launchers (TELs), missiles and fire control radar, deliveries starting 2020.<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://thediplomat.com/2016/10/india-and-russia-ink-s-400-missile-air-defense-system-deal/|title=India and Russia Ink S-400 Missile Air Defense System Deal|last=Diplomat|first=Franz-Stefan Gady, The|newspaper=The Diplomat|access-date=2016-10-27}}</ref> \n|-S-400 -five regiments of S-400 air defense systems\n|[[MRSAM|Barak-8]]\n|[[File:Barak 8 launcher.jpg|center|frameless]]\n|[[Surface-to-air missile]]\n|0\n|{{Flagu|India}}<br>{{Flagu|Israel}}\n|'''Status: On Order. ''' Medium Range Surface to Air Missile. .<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.ibtimes.co.in/pm-modi-clears-deal-india-army-acquire-vital-air-defence-systems-israel-soon-717125|title=India clears deal; army to acquire air defence systems from Israel soon|last=Bhat|first=Aditya|newspaper=International Business Times, India Edition|access-date=2017-02-24|language=en|url-status=live|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170224011717/http://www.ibtimes.co.in/pm-modi-clears-deal-india-army-acquire-vital-air-defence-systems-israel-soon-717125|archivedate=