-117082600691_1.html|title=Arun Jaitley inaugurates manufacture of light combat helicopter at HAL|date=27 August 2017|accessdate=21 December 2017}}</ref><br>5 LCH to be procured under LSP.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/hal-gets-order-for-15-light-combat-helicopters/article22260545.ece|title=HAL gets order for 15 Light Combat Helicopters|date=22 December 2017|accessdate=25 December 2017}}</ref> Total 114 on order.<ref name=\"Flightglobal\" /> It has completed all initial tests. Trials of missile firing were held in mid 2016.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.indiandefensenews.in/2016/03/hals-lch-passes-rocket-trials-will.html|title=HAL'S LCH PASSES ROCKET TRIALS|last=|first=|date=2016-03-16|website=INDIANDEFENSE NEWS|publisher=INDIANDEFENSE NEWS|access-date=}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[HAL Rudra]] || [[File:HAL Rudra at Aero India 2013.JPG|200px]] || {{IND}} || [[Attack helicopter]] || ALH-WSI || 50 || 50 in service with 10 more on order<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.newindianexpress.com/nation/2019/oct/08/army-boosting-combat-fighting-capabilities-with-major-inductions-of-indigenous-helicopters-2044607.html|title=Army boosting combat fighting capabilities with major inductions of indigenous helicopters|website=The New Indian Express|access-date=2020-03-01}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[HAL Dhruv]] || [[File:IA-1136 HAL Dhruv (Indian Army).jpg|200px]] || {{IND}} || [[Utility helicopter]] ||  || 145<ref name=\"Flightglobal\"/> || Total of 264 on order.<ref name=\"Flightglobal\"/>\n|-\n|[[Kamov Ka-226]]\n|[[File:Kamov Ka-226 MAKS 2005.jpg|200x200px]]\n|{{Flagu|India}}<br>{{Flagu|Russia}}\n|[[Utility helicopter]]\n|Ka-226T\n|\n| 200 to be built in India at HAL Helicopter Manufacturing plant being built at Tumkuru.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.indiandefensenews.in/2015/08/make-in-india-russia-wants-co.html|title=MAKE IN INDIA: RUSSIA WANTS CO-PRODUCTION OF KA-226 CHOPPERS TO START AS SOON AS POSSIBLE|last=|first=|date=2015-08-29|website=INDIANDEFENSE NEWS|publisher=INDIA